{"tid":1482363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[開定先] 818 之後點，以下開放討論","createTime":"2019-08-18T05:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:23:18.000Z","uid":123933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1be723637236af1ce98b2c07304c7a126d65352","tid":1482363,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"今日最後可能係所有人散，可能有部份人會be water 地set roadblock / 圍狗屋，可能有臥底狗拉鳩人。<br />\n<br />\n唔理最後結果點，我地係時候要諗下，咁818之後條路要點行？<br />\n<br />\n兩個月了，差不多咩都試過晒，中共港共受盡壓力，都依然係強硬心態，<br />\n<br />\n反之，我地做嘅野越來越無效，現實情況嚟講，亦都多咗好多內鬥嘅事例出現咗（例如勇武和理非又互罵）。<br />\n<br />\n宜家我地贏唔到，係因為所謂嘅沉默大多數仍然係佔主流。我地嚟緊要做嘅野，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">就係要盡力令100%香港人都企係我地個邊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔想再係街聽代有人屌我地。<br />\n我唔想香港再有黃藍之別。<br />\n場仗有排打，要打到2047都可能未完。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要令香港再無黃藍之分，只有民主自由 v.s. 極權中共之分</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ef32716916256deb8864dc8f7512a4661d67ef4","tid":1482363,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"［海外文宣新方向］激起各國本土意識 抵制中國貨及中資企業<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1482245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1482245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4a2813d4974bf87c7170fd7adeb1704a095d196","tid":1482363,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">風雨不改！2PM！WAI YUEN GIN！ </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrJrLgG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrJrLgG.jpg&h=d354981c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMZbbWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMZbbWG.jpg&h=b5e6b6ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"691724d0c814ddc7173fc40a1db54c535d5b350b","tid":1482363,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}